# /config — Environment-aware application configuration
# Centralizes all external config (DB, JWT, CORS, rate-limits, third-party keys).
# Examples:
#   index.js       → Merges .env values into a typed config object
#   db.js          → PostgreSQL connection pool (pg / Sequelize / Knex) setup
#   cors.js        → Allowed origins, methods, headers
#   logger.js      → Winston/Pino logger transport configuration
#   redis.js       → Redis client for caching & session store (if applicable)
